{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"41":{"eng-name":"Types of Blood-Wit (Kitab Al-Diyat)","ara-name":"كتاب الديات"}},"section_detail":{"41":{"hadithnumber_first":4494,"hadithnumber_last":4595,"arabicnumber_first":4494,"arabicnumber_last":4595}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4571,"arabicnumber":4571,"text":"حدثنا موسى بن اسماعيل، حدثنا وهيب، عن هشام، عن ابيه، عن المغيرة، عن عمر، بمعناه . قال ابو داود رواه حماد بن زيد وحماد بن سلمة عن هشام بن عروة، عن ابيه، ان عمر، قال","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (6905)"}],"reference":{"book":41,"hadith":78},"chapter":{"id":21,"ara-name":"باب دِيَةِ الْجَنِينِ","eng-name":"The Diyah For A Fetus","isFirstHadith":false}}]}